    "In 1989 the third edition of the Constable/Links monograph appeared with Links as an acknowledged co-author.": [],
    "The same year the Metropolitan Museum in New York launched a major Canaletto exhibition, organized by Links.": [],
    "Beginning in the 1960s, he became involved in the establishment of the Venice in Peril Fund, a fundraising group for repairing the sinking city.": [],
    "He died at his London home in 1997.</p>": []
